OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA mixed day of bright spells
OL,6,Fand blustery showers, best of the dry
OL,7,Fand bright spells will be in the east.
OL,8,FStrong southerly winds which may reach
OL,9,Fgale force.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,12,Fspells and a few showers Monday.
OL,13,FLargely dry with sunny spells Tuesday.
OL,14,FMostly cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,15,Fon Wednesday. Winds light Monday then
OL,16,Fbreezy on Tuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
